reviews.review_text:
now i'm a believer after having loved this at the show, i then had a cruddy aud and doubted my allegiance from time to time.  after hearing this recording, now i know that it wasn't just the hubris of having been there for the show.

this terrapin is for real, one of the all-time greats.  again, for the doubtful: terrapin->drumz->space->playin' reprise.  it's more than worth the price of admission.

llr's a nice nugget, too.
